==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fireman
<hw>Fire"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Firemen</plw> <pr>(-m<it>e</it>n)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
man whose business is to extinguish fires in towns; a member of a fire
company.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A man who tends the fires, as of a steam engine; a
stocker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fire-new</ent>⟦br⟧
